# Expert Sources – AI-Powered SEO Content Production

This document lists 10 high-signal practitioners whose work focuses on AI-assisted SEO and scalable content production. Each entry includes key content pieces and a short note on why they were selected.

---

## 1. Neil Patel – Co-founder, NP Digital

- Profile: https://neilpatel.com/ 

**Key pieces**

- “Leverage AI-Powered SEO for Content Production & Strategy” (2025-03-31) – Article outlining how to use AI for research, outlining, drafting, editing, and refreshing SEO content, plus a quality-control checklist.   
- Various blog posts on content marketing and SEO experimentation with AI-assisted workflows. 
**Why chosen**

Neil runs a large SEO/content agency and writes specifically about how AI plugs into each stage of an SEO content pipeline, including guardrails for quality and brand voice.
